name: MARYTREES BEATS #1 "Let's Go Branden NFT POP-UP Shop" (All other (Unofficial) spellings (ie "BRANDON") are now illegal under US CODE 420.69). x/1776 HISTORICAL EDITIONS for 1.776 XTZ.
description: This is our first piece in our Marytrees Beats series. These are Marytrees Beat Loops with custom visuals and a central theme. This piece is intended as a historical record to document the cultural phenomenon of the "Let's Go Brandon" movement. To celebrate our first piece we're making an unusually high number of 1776 editions available. Enjoy!
